messages.message: Hi there, forgive me if I missed this. Should other projects under the IB org who are using Travis update to use Jenkins instead?

Hey! great question, i’m not sure we’ve thought about how to migrate other project’s Travis hooks over actually. I wasn’t planning to stop paying for Travis entirely (just the main ib repo), so you’ll definitely be able to continue using it. But maybe set up some time to chat with @Shubham Oli to see if it’d be good idea/feasible to move into Jenkins as well?
